name: Soft Pink Orbitals
description:
Add a gentle flair to your ensemble. Handmade with white glass seed beads and pastel pink coated glass pearls, this piece provides a perfect accent for both day and evening wear. 

These beautiful light-weight earrings are approximately 2" in diameter. Surgical steel and titanium are used for the earring posts, catering to those with sensitive ears.

name: Hotpink & Ivory Orbitals
description:
Blazing hot pink seed beads, with contrasting ivory colored beads, make these earrings an excellent show stopper in every environment, whether casual or semi-formal. 

These beautiful light-weight earrings are approximately 2" in diameter. Surgical steel and titanium are used for the earring posts, catering to those with sensitive ears.

name: Goldstone Love Earrings
description:
Handmade with casual elegance, the beautiful shimmer of these earrings add the perfect accent for day/evening attire.

Goldstone is a copper based, man made stone that has many healing attributes, which includes strengthening Chi as well as promoting a calm and positive state of well being. 

These beautiful light-weight earrings are approximately 2" in diameter. Surgical steel and titanium are used for the earring posts, catering to those with sensitive ears.
